# EmailJS Configuration
# 1. Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com/
# 2. Create an Email Service (e.g. Gmail, Outlook)
# 3. Create the main Email Template with these variables:
#    {{from_name}} {{from_email}} {{project_type}} {{brief}}
# 4. Create an Auto-Reply Template (To Email = {{from_email}}) with:
#    {{from_name}} {{project_type}} {{brief}}
# 5. Copy your IDs below and rename this file to ".env"

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_AUTOREPLY_TEMPLATE_ID=your_autoreply_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
